Error: Either --repo or --archive is required
Usage: ploy arf transform [options]

Transform code with recipes and/or LLM-powered self-healing

Input Sources (one required):
  --repo <url>           Repository URL to transform
  --archive <path>       Archive path (alternative to repo)

Transformation (at least one required):
  --recipes <ids>        Comma-separated recipe IDs
  --prompts <prompts>    Comma-separated LLM prompts
  --recipe <id>          Single recipe ID (can be repeated)
  --prompt <prompt>      Single LLM prompt (can be repeated)

LLM Configuration:
  --plan-model <model>   LLM for planning (default: ollama/codellama:7b)
  --exec-model <model>   LLM for execution (default: ollama/codellama:7b)

Execution Parameters:
  --max-iterations <n>   Max retries per error (default: 3)
  --parallel-tries <n>   Parallel solution attempts (default: 3)
  --timeout <duration>   Timeout per iteration (default: 5m)

Output Configuration:
  --output <format>      archive|diff|mr (default: diff)
  --output-path <path>   Where to save output
  --report <level>       minimal|standard|detailed (default: standard)

Additional Options:
  --branch <name>        Git branch (default: main)
  --app-name <name>      Application name for deployment testing
  --lane <lane>          Deployment lane (auto-detected if not specified)

Examples:
  # Apply Java 17 migration recipe
  ploy arf transform --repo https://github.com/example/app --recipe java11to17

  # Apply multiple recipes with detailed reporting
  ploy arf transform --repo https://github.com/example/app \
    --recipes java11to17,spring-boot-3 --report detailed

  # LLM-driven transformation with custom prompt
  ploy arf transform --repo https://github.com/example/app \
    --prompt "Migrate from JUnit 4 to JUnit 5" --output archive
